:14:33.000Z","msg":"蘋果教主死前都話後悔用另類療法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1372bdc9dae8743c96b9cf0b74ebdd469df7ff7a","tid":1106871,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"召喚自然療法撚同中醫撚"},{"pid":"e6714f71db1a155f09aebdfd0d1e70b966e98465","tid":1106871,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"其實講真，呢d誰對誰錯冇人知。<br />\n因為無人有時光機可以對比，話大家知唔用另類療法真係會好左。<br />\n但係, 我覺得scientific studies 比出來的証據會比好多另類療法好。<br />\n一向cancer 唔係隻隻醫得好，好多都係講緊五年存活率，甚少用cure 呢個字眼。"},{"pid":"5fca04c7591e4adca194e6a42ecd6d12ac1ee188","tid":1106871,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"又咪想人用標靶藥拖幾年命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}